message.content: "cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR". The paper focuses on visual dialog, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) and "cs.CV" (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses pretraining and deep neural models, which are common in "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) sub-categories. Finally, the paper also discusses metrics and analysis, which could fall under "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval).
